===UI installation & settings for Ubuntu===

Requred packages:
- apache2
- mariadb

Settings:

APACHE
- copy devtools/taskbot/core/conf/apache_taskbot.conf to /etc/apache2/sites-enabled and change it:
  * Change VirtualHost address & port or ServerName;
  * Set ServiceAlias (optional);
  * Set valid paths for logs & public_html
- enable cgi module (sudo a2enmod cgi) & restart apache (service apache2 restart).
- prepare public_html:
          |-- commons (devtools/taskbot/ui/commons)
          |-- taskbot (devtools/taskbot/ui)

MYSQL
- Change /etc/mysql/my.cnf:
  * max_allowed_packet	= 16M
- Ensure that mysql service were started (service mysql status).
- Create taskbot database:
  * sudo -i mysql --user=root mysql < devtools/taskbot/core/sql/initial.mysql
  * mysql --user=taskbot --password=taskbot taskbot <  devtools/taskbot/core/sql/schema.mysql

Debbuging
- use 'trace' parameter for taskbot.py script to view full output.
- use TASKBOT_DEBUG_MODE to strict email notification:
  1 - send notification to taskbot owner only
  2 - send notification to taskbot & watchers (skip commiters).


